sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  box rgb(255,228,220) Authored order system
    participant Caller
    participant Graph as Order workflow
    participant OrderActor as Order actor
    participant Audit as Detached audit task
  end
  box rgb(240,242,244) Explicit providers
    participant Providers as Payment, inventory, risk and shipping
  end
  box rgb(238,229,247) Contained runtime
    participant Chamber
  end
  box rgb(220,236,255) Trusted distributed substrate
    participant Cell
  end
  box rgb(255,242,204) Durable authority and state
    participant Authority
  end
  box rgb(223,245,242) Interpretation
    participant Evidence
  end

  Caller->>Graph: inquire submit-order
  Graph->>Graph: validate, price and compose parallel decisions
  Graph->>Providers: explicit payment, inventory and risk boundaries
  Providers-->>Graph: deterministic success or domain failure
  alt Business decisions succeed
    Graph->>OrderActor: strict write-through order mutation
    OrderActor->>Chamber: execute actor task under assignment epoch
    Chamber->>Cell: mediated actor persistence capability
    Cell->>Authority: commit exact version and assignment epoch
    Authority-->>Cell: durable receipt
    Cell-->>Chamber: committed outcome
    Chamber-->>OrderActor: new state
    Graph-->>Caller: composed order result
    Graph-->>Audit: detached signal, same overarching trace
  else Provider decline or stock conflict
    Graph-->>Caller: explicit domain failure and no false committed order
  end
  Chamber->>Evidence: bounded execution and context commitments
  Cell->>Evidence: distribution, custody and recovery evidence
  opt Actor owner is lost later
    Authority->>Cell: assignment epoch N+1
    Cell->>Chamber: successor residency and hydration
    Chamber->>Authority: continue from committed state
    Evidence-->>Caller: failure and recovery remain traceable
  end
